210
00:17:56,575 --> 00:17:59,119
You won't back off no matter what, right?

211
00:18:04,917 --> 00:18:06,585
Did you even hear what I said?

212
00:18:07,586 --> 00:18:09,797
Of course I won't back off.

213
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,507
What do you want me to say?

214
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:16,053
You can't avoid it even if you want to.

215
00:18:16,136 --> 00:18:18,305
Nothing will change if I stop.

216
00:18:18,388 --> 00:18:21,475
I should at least keep going
to get something out of it, right?

217
00:18:24,686 --> 00:18:27,564
I don't know what's at the end
of this investigation,

218
00:18:27,648 --> 00:18:29,650
but we'll see when we get there.

219
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:36,865
I'll stop him from doing anything.

220
00:18:37,783 --> 00:18:39,284
I'll do whatever I can

221
00:18:40,327 --> 00:18:42,663
to stop him from investigating.

222
00:18:43,747 --> 00:18:45,374
I'll get it done this time.

223
00:18:47,334 --> 00:18:48,836
